<paragraph id="CCAAE91FF4E5167E854271454B64C887" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="AE1E201F4964392037FFCC57A2C6586E" class="Demospongiae" family="Chondrillidae" genus="Chondrilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chondrillida" pageId="null" pageNumber="590" phylum="Porifera" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="578EB53F8F3C9416B5EE51866BD91ED6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">Chondrilla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(S. 624) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="9941174F6F991F21F13352E315D17ACE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">
<normalizedToken id="204E5AE2FDDB9CB6ADDE81CAA8E677FE" originalValue="Köpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">Koepfe</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="39009F417B81AFAB73126639911E28D5" originalValue="vielblütig" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">vielbluetig</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken id="31BA918971B52E0EDE203DB7566773EC" originalValue="Hülle" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">Huelle</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="6AEC2E65F62FCD4944C1C65B7965C1E9" originalValue="glockenförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">glockenfoermig</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4C16CCF22E6ED80E3305C8B07D839183" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">
Die Gattung 
<taxonomicName id="A8FE6FBEC9817ABC98C60971E2305766" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Willemetia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="590" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="9D7D52FA35D7572F69A3AA716E533814" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">Willemetia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="8996B14FCDCE7D2709C9E819BA551A18" originalValue="umfaßt" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">umfasst</normalizedToken>
nur 2 Arten, wovon die eine (
<taxonomicName id="A2BDC2DD130498C4211F8F5456664712" authority="Fisch" authorityName="Fisch" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Thrincia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="590" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="tuberosa">
<emphasis id="82720C70559D24BE55937DDC43BE5277" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="590">W. tuberosa</emphasis>
Fisch
</taxonomicName>
, et Mey.) im Kaukasus vorkommt.
</paragraph>
